Technical accuracy — factual correctness
Depth of knowledge — going beyond surface-level answers
Relevance — staying on topic
Problem-solving — logical, structured thinking
Use of examples — grounding answers in real experience
Critical thinking — weighing trade-offs and nuance
Honesty — give grace to honest replies to 'i dont know'
Adaptability — honesty about gaps and openness to learning
Conciseness — complete but focused answers